English: <color=red>://ERROR: Door in emergency lockdown. Door requires power from a generator in</color> <color=orange>ZONE 121</color>.
Description:
Don't localize ZONE 121.
A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.
